verbose_text: Concern has been raised over the stability of the JBL carbon store as climate models predict an increase in mean annual air temperature of 3-4degreesC by 2020 and 5-10degreesC by 2050, with only minor increases in precipitation of 10-20% in this region by the end of the twenty-first century.
